The paper deals with active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) that involves selecting the most informative examples to label. The paper also deals with partial feedback, which is relevant to several other subfields of machine learning, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
